Component,Platform,Why it's best for you
Database,Supabase or Aiven,Supabase offers a professional PostgreSQL DB that handles 50k rows easily. Aiven offers a free 5GB plan which is huge.
Backend,Render or Koyeb,"Both allow you to deploy Spring Boot for free. Koyeb is faster for Java, while Render is very beginner-friendly."
Frontend,Netlify or Vercel,"They provide a Permanent HTTPS Link (e.g., attendance-system.netlify.app) for free."
